3
00:00:36.512 --> 00:00:40.107
[crowd cheers]

4
00:01:25.594 --> 00:01:30.088
[chanting]

5
00:01:38.174 --> 00:01:40.506
[crowd cheers]

6
00:01:53.356 --> 00:01:57.656
These are the days of our great lament.

7
00:01:57.727 --> 00:01:59.957
[crowd shouting indistinctly]

8
00:02:02.131 --> 00:02:04.031
The land thirsts.

9
00:02:06.469 --> 00:02:10.872
A great plague infests our crops.

10
00:02:13.709 --> 00:02:17.770
The scourge of sickness
afflicts us at whim.

11
00:02:23.786 --> 00:02:27.381
They say this strife has made us weak.

12
00:02:29.625 --> 00:02:31.456
That we have become empty.

13
00:02:34.263 --> 00:02:36.527
They say that we rot.

14
00:02:48.244 --> 00:02:51.111
Great people of the banner of the sun...

15
00:02:51.947 --> 00:02:53.414
I say...

16
00:02:54.617 --> 00:02:56.414
...we are strong.

17
00:03:00.923 --> 00:03:02.982
We are a people of destiny.

18
00:03:07.797 --> 00:03:11.062
Destined to be the masters of time.

19
00:03:15.137 --> 00:03:18.402
Destined to be nearest to the gods.

20
00:03:34.356 --> 00:03:37.484
Mighty Kukulkan!

21
00:03:39.128 --> 00:03:43.656
Whose fury could scorch
this earth to oblivion...

22
00:03:46.302 --> 00:03:48.600
Let us appease you with this sacrifice.

23
00:03:49.205 --> 00:03:51.002
To exalt you in your glory.

24
00:03:51.874 --> 00:03:54.468
To make our people prosper.

25
00:03:55.578 --> 00:03:58.308
To prepare for your return.

26
00:04:01.383 --> 00:04:04.147
Warrior. unafraid and willing!

27
00:04:04.720 --> 00:04:07.052
With your blood you renew the world!

28
00:04:07.590 --> 00:04:09.387
From age to age.

29
00:04:10.826 --> 00:04:12.453
Thanks be to you.

30
00:04:12.528 --> 00:04:14.758
- [crowd cheers]
- [gasping]

31
00:04:27.209 --> 00:04:29.370
The heart of god!

32
00:04:45.628 --> 00:04:47.721
[chanting]

33
00:05:41.950 --> 00:05:46.284
- [heartbeat pounding]
- [speaking in Mayan]

34
00:06:11.446 --> 00:06:13.744
[gasping]

35
00:06:48.416 --> 00:06:50.646
[inhales sharply]

36
00:07:13.074 --> 00:07:15.338
Come back to me.

37
00:07:24.285 --> 00:07:26.150
Brother...

38
00:07:28.056 --> 00:07:29.853
Journey well...

39
00:07:32.026 --> 00:07:32.924
No.

40
00:07:34.429 --> 00:07:35.555
I can't go.

41
00:07:37.098 --> 00:07:38.656
Not now...

42
00:07:49.978 --> 00:07:52.378
[man speaks indistinctly]

43
00:08:04.359 --> 00:08:05.690
[giggles]

44
00:08:37.692 --> 00:08:41.958
[warbled chanting]

45
00:09:00.148 --> 00:09:03.515
[crowd moaning]

46
00:09:34.315 --> 00:09:37.113
[crowd wailing]

47
00:09:58.406 --> 00:10:03.241
People of the banner
of the sun do not fear.

48
00:10:04.178 --> 00:10:06.009
Rejoice!

49
00:10:07.281 --> 00:10:10.307
Kukulkan has drunk his fill of blood.

50
00:10:10.685 --> 00:10:13.483
We have sated his thirst.

51
00:10:14.622 --> 00:10:16.317
Great god.

52
00:10:17.291 --> 00:10:19.521
Show us that you are pleased.

53
00:10:19.794 --> 00:10:23.389
Let your light return upon us.

54
00:10:30.271 --> 00:10:32.432
[all cheer]

55
00:10:48.389 --> 00:10:53.053
- [muttering]
- [laughing]

56
00:11:28.763 --> 00:11:30.822
What of these captives?

57
00:11:35.536 --> 00:11:37.436
Dispose of them.

58
00:11:39.774 --> 00:11:41.901
- [shouting indistinctly]
- [men panting]

59
00:12:11.873 --> 00:12:14.034
I need a finisher.

60
00:12:19.080 --> 00:12:20.377
You.

61
00:12:26.487 --> 00:12:28.045
Release them.

62
00:12:36.330 --> 00:12:37.957
You watch.

63
00:12:45.973 --> 00:12:47.440
- [gasps]
- [grunts]

64
00:12:58.853 --> 00:12:59.911
I'm ready!

65
00:13:04.926 --> 00:13:07.895
There's your jungle beyond the corn.

66
00:13:10.865 --> 00:13:12.264
Go to it.

67
00:13:13.100 --> 00:13:14.499
You're free...

68
00:13:16.370 --> 00:13:17.735
...now run.

69
00:13:21.075 --> 00:13:22.406
I said run.

70
00:13:26.814 --> 00:13:28.076
Run!

71
00:14:00.081 --> 00:14:01.912
- [grunts]
- [men cheer]

72
00:14:05.086 --> 00:14:08.920
[shuddering]

73
00:14:41.722 --> 00:14:42.814
Not bad.

74
00:14:45.960 --> 00:14:47.825
[gasping heavily]

75
00:15:00.975 --> 00:15:02.306
Your turn.

76
00:15:10.151 --> 00:15:11.675
Run.

77
00:15:19.226 --> 00:15:21.319
[panting]

78
00:16:08.442 --> 00:16:10.672
[all cheer]

79
00:16:14.782 --> 00:16:18.115
[straining]

80
00:16:27.561 --> 00:16:29.028
Run!

81
00:16:50.251 --> 00:16:52.685
- [grunts]
- [men laugh]

82
00:17:01.262 --> 00:17:03.628
[men muttering]

83
00:17:43.537 --> 00:17:45.095
Sleep.

84
00:17:46.073 --> 00:17:48.303
Sleep. sleep now my son.

85
00:17:49.376 --> 00:17:51.708
The pain will be no more.

86
00:17:53.681 --> 00:17:54.943
Sleep.

87
00:18:30.017 --> 00:18:32.747
[all hollering]

88
00:19:26.240 --> 00:19:27.867
[panting]

89
00:19:49.263 --> 00:19:52.391
- [shouts]
- [flies buzzing]

90
00:21:34.435 --> 00:21:37.427
[gasping. groaning]

91
00:23:04.792 --> 00:23:08.455
[animal growls]

92
00:23:13.400 --> 00:23:17.131
[animal snarls loudly]

93
00:23:45.032 --> 00:23:47.159
He didn't come this way.

94
00:24:00.447 --> 00:24:02.415
He's in the trees.

95
00:24:04.184 --> 00:24:05.412
Spread out.

96
00:24:06.286 --> 00:24:07.810
Keep your eyes up.

97
00:24:26.139 --> 00:24:27.333
[growling]

98
00:24:30.210 --> 00:24:31.268
Quiet.

99
00:24:38.151 --> 00:24:40.415
[leaves rustling]

100
00:24:42.890 --> 00:24:44.084
He's coming right at us.

101
00:24:56.069 --> 00:24:58.663
[rapid footsteps approaching]

102
00:25:00.807 --> 00:25:01.466
There!

103
00:25:44.518 --> 00:25:48.010
- [snarling]
- [screaming]

104
00:26:06.707 --> 00:26:08.470
[yelling. grunting]

105
00:26:27.861 --> 00:26:31.194
[rumbling]

106
00:26:59.693 --> 00:27:02.423
He would have wanted me to have it.

107
00:27:04.598 --> 00:27:07.533
The omen is bad...

108
00:27:09.469 --> 00:27:12.529
Mighty Ek Chuah we beg you...

109
00:27:13.807 --> 00:27:18.039
Forgive us for this trespass
against your son the Jaguar.

110
00:27:20.047 --> 00:27:22.538
The omen is bad...

111
00:27:24.284 --> 00:27:26.252
Lift yourself up Drunkards Four...

112
00:27:27.120 --> 00:27:30.112
...the omen was foretold...

113
00:27:32.492 --> 00:27:35.689
...and now we have a fear more grave...

114
00:27:36.663 --> 00:27:40.064
...today I saw the day
become like night...

115
00:27:45.038 --> 00:27:46.528
[grunts]

116
00:27:46.606 --> 00:27:50.235
I saw a man run with the Jaguar...

117
00:27:54.147 --> 00:27:58.243
...we must not let this man
make feet from us.

118
00:27:58.985 --> 00:28:00.145
[man] Enough.

119
00:28:03.924 --> 00:28:05.789
Your words mean nothing.

120
00:28:07.160 --> 00:28:09.390
He runs because he is afraid.

121
00:28:10.764 --> 00:28:14.393
When I catch him.
I will peel his skin...

122
00:28:17.437 --> 00:28:20.167
...and have him watch me wear it.

123
00:28:27.881 --> 00:28:29.109
We leave now.

124
00:29:08.121 --> 00:29:10.180
[panting. straining]

125
00:29:14.361 --> 00:29:17.091
- [thudding]
- [gasping]

126
00:29:59.072 --> 00:30:01.233
[dog barking]

127
00:30:20.560 --> 00:30:21.891
- [snarling]
- [gasping]

128
00:30:34.140 --> 00:30:36.665
- [thudding]
- [whimpering]

129
00:30:36.743 --> 00:30:37.937
Stay back.

130
00:31:11.845 --> 00:31:14.245
- [squealing]
- [shouting]

131
00:31:33.867 --> 00:31:35.960
- [panting]
- [uneven footsteps running]

132
00:31:48.882 --> 00:31:50.008
Here!

133
00:31:59.059 --> 00:32:01.220
[yelping. moaning]

134
00:32:03.997 --> 00:32:06.158
[wheezing]

135
00:32:14.574 --> 00:32:16.701
The omen was bad...

136
00:32:20.413 --> 00:32:21.539
He's fucked.

137
00:32:24.851 --> 00:32:26.250
Help... please...

138
00:32:27.087 --> 00:32:28.349
Hanging Moss...

139
00:32:30.023 --> 00:32:31.650
See him out.

140
00:32:52.112 --> 00:32:55.775
Open your veins. It's quicker.

141
00:33:08.495 --> 00:33:10.588
Travel well.

142
00:35:42.882 --> 00:35:44.873
[exhaling heavily]

143
00:36:16.416 --> 00:36:19.146
So much for your prophecies.

144
00:36:25.024 --> 00:36:26.252
It's not over!

145
00:36:35.501 --> 00:36:37.731
[gasping]

146
00:36:52.285 --> 00:36:53.912
I am Jaguar Paw...

147
00:36:54.621 --> 00:36:56.179
Son of Flint Sky...

148
00:36:57.624 --> 00:37:00.991
My father hunted
this forest before me...

149
00:37:02.729 --> 00:37:04.697
My name is Jaguar Paw.

150
00:37:05.531 --> 00:37:07.123
I am a hunter.

151
00:37:08.735 --> 00:37:10.999
This is my forest.

152
00:37:12.171 --> 00:37:16.699
And my sons will hunt it
with their sons after I am gone...

153
00:37:19.579 --> 00:37:20.807
Come on!

154
00:37:23.483 --> 00:37:25.178
We are going over.

155
00:37:25.752 --> 00:37:28.482
We climb down around.

156
00:37:29.756 --> 00:37:31.849
We cannot let him get away.

157
00:37:32.558 --> 00:37:33.684
We cannot afford...

158
00:37:33.760 --> 00:37:36.126
[gasping]

159
00:37:53.913 --> 00:37:56.040
We all jump.

160
00:38:00.253 --> 00:38:03.154
[shouting]

161
00:38:21.007 --> 00:38:23.373
[gasps]

162
00:39:14.460 --> 00:39:16.985
- [gulping]
- [mud bubbling]

163
00:39:53.399 --> 00:39:55.424
[inhaling sharply]

164
00:40:26.265 --> 00:40:30.258
[panting]

165
00:40:53.059 --> 00:40:54.686
I am Jaguar Paw.

166
00:40:56.562 --> 00:40:58.393
This is my forest.

167
00:41:00.466 --> 00:41:03.162
And I am not afraid.

168
00:41:18.918 --> 00:41:22.081
[buzzing]

169
00:41:42.742 --> 00:41:45.108
[all screaming]

170
00:43:10.596 --> 00:43:13.156
You go. I'll wait here.

171
00:44:07.319 --> 00:44:11.517
[wheezing]

172
00:45:15.421 --> 00:45:17.912
- [thunder rumbles]
- [gasping]

173
00:45:43.816 --> 00:45:46.011
[straining]

174
00:45:49.588 --> 00:45:51.852
- [gasps]
- [wails]

175
00:46:23.455 --> 00:46:25.855
[wheezing]

176
00:46:30.863 --> 00:46:33.593
- [blows]
- [winces]

177
00:46:52.318 --> 00:46:53.785
[moans. yells]

178
00:47:30.456 --> 00:47:36.452
[both breathing heavily]

179
00:48:27.313 --> 00:48:31.477
[wheezing]

180
00:48:42.695 --> 00:48:44.492
Almost...

181
00:48:58.177 --> 00:49:01.772
[thundering]

182
00:49:11.357 --> 00:49:14.053
Resting fathers. fly me your strength.

183
00:49:22.034 --> 00:49:23.023
[growls]

184
00:49:33.746 --> 00:49:39.582
- [shivering]
- [crying]

185
00:49:41.086 --> 00:49:42.849
Get up here.

186
00:49:47.826 --> 00:49:51.159
- [gasps. grunting]
- [yelling]

187
00:49:57.736 --> 00:49:59.294
Go back!

188
00:50:26.632 --> 00:50:28.623
- [gasping]
- [speaks Mayan]

189
00:50:28.700 --> 00:50:29.394
Quick!

190
00:50:30.002 --> 00:50:30.969
Hurry up!

191
00:50:31.804 --> 00:50:33.101
[arrow whizzing]

192
00:50:46.218 --> 00:50:47.981
[straining]

193
00:51:18.383 --> 00:51:20.374
[gasps]

194
00:52:36.562 --> 00:52:39.156
[exhales]

195
00:53:49.434 --> 00:53:53.268
[pushing]

196
00:54:21.066 --> 00:54:25.264
- [crying]
- [gulping]

197
00:56:16.515 --> 00:56:19.882
[baby wailing]

198
00:56:57.823 --> 00:56:59.688
What are they?

199
00:57:01.359 --> 00:57:03.190
They bring men.

200
00:57:07.833 --> 00:57:09.733
Should we go to them?

201
00:57:18.043 --> 00:57:19.840
We should go to the forest.

202
00:57:26.751 --> 00:57:28.651
To seek a new beginning.

203
00:57:33.792 --> 00:57:35.225
Come Turtles Run...

204
00:57:36.305 --> 00:58:36.227
